{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.1","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:1","prev_osis_id":"Luke.011.054,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Instructions de J\u00e9sus sur: \u2014 l\u2019hypocrisie, \u2014 la crainte des hommes, \u2014 le blasph\u00e8me contre le Saint-Esprit, \u2014 l\u2019avarice, \u2014 la confiance dans les richesses (parabole de l\u2019homme riche), \u2014 les inqui\u00e9tudes, \u2014 l\u2019aum\u00f4ne, \u2014 la vigilance, \u2014 les signes des temps, \u2014 la r\u00e9conciliation<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-12: cf. Mt 16:6-12; 10:16-39.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Sur ces entrefaites, les gens s\u2019\u00e9tant rassembl\u00e9s par milliers, au point de se fouler les uns les autres, J\u00e9sus se mit \u00e0 dire \u00e0 ses disciples: <span class=\"wj\">Avant tout, gardez-vous du levain des pharisiens, qui est l\u2019hypocrisie.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.2","name":"Luc 12:2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.11.54","name":"Luc 11:54","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.11.54"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.2","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:2","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il n\u2019y a rien de cach\u00e9 qui ne doive \u00eatre d\u00e9couvert, ni de secret qui ne doive \u00eatre connu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.3","name":"Luc 12:3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.1","name":"Luc 12:1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.3","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:3","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est pourquoi tout ce que vous aurez dit dans les t\u00e9n\u00e8bres sera entendu dans la lumi\u00e8re, et ce que vous aurez dit \u00e0 l\u2019oreille dans les chambres sera pr\u00each\u00e9 sur les toits.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.4","name":"Luc 12:4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.2","name":"Luc 12:2","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.4","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:4","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous dis, \u00e0 vous qui \u00eates mes amis:<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Ne craignez pas ceux qui tuent le corps et qui, apr\u00e8s cela, ne peuvent rien faire de plus.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.5","name":"Luc 12:5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.3","name":"Luc 12:3","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.5","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:5","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous montrerai qui vous devez craindre. Craignez celui qui, apr\u00e8s avoir tu\u00e9, a le pouvoir de jeter dans la g\u00e9henne; oui, je vous le dis, c\u2019est lui que vous devez craindre.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.6","name":"Luc 12:6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.4","name":"Luc 12:4","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.6","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:6","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne vend-on pas cinq passereaux pour deux sous? Cependant, aucun d\u2019eux n\u2019est oubli\u00e9 devant Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.7","name":"Luc 12:7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.5","name":"Luc 12:5","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.7","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:7","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et m\u00eame les cheveux de votre t\u00eate sont tous compt\u00e9s. Ne craignez donc point: vous valez plus que beaucoup de passereaux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.8","name":"Luc 12:8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.6","name":"Luc 12:6","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.8","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:8","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis, quiconque me confessera devant les hommes, le Fils de l\u2019homme le confessera aussi devant les anges de Dieu;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.9","name":"Luc 12:9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.7","name":"Luc 12:7","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.9","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:9","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">mais celui qui me reniera devant les hommes sera reni\u00e9 devant les anges de Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.10","name":"Luc 12:10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.8","name":"Luc 12:8","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.10","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:10","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et quiconque parlera contre le Fils de l\u2019homme, il lui sera pardonn\u00e9;<\/span><span class=\"wj\">mais \u00e0 celui qui blasph\u00e9mera contre le Saint-Esprit il ne sera point pardonn\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.11","name":"Luc 12:11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.9","name":"Luc 12:9","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.11","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:11","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Quand on vous m\u00e8nera devant les synagogues, les magistrats et les autorit\u00e9s, ne vous inqui\u00e9tez pas de la mani\u00e8re dont vous vous d\u00e9fendrez ni de ce que vous direz;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.12","name":"Luc 12:12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.10","name":"Luc 12:10","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.12","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:12","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">car le Saint-Esprit vous enseignera \u00e0 l\u2019heure m\u00eame ce qu\u2019il faudra dire.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.13","name":"Luc 12:13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.11","name":"Luc 12:11","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.13","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:13","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.014,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 13-21: cf. (Ps 49; 73.) Mt 16:26. Lu 16:19-26. J\u00e9 9:23. Ec 8:8; 9:12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Quelqu\u2019un dit \u00e0 J\u00e9sus, du milieu de la foule: Ma\u00eetre, dis \u00e0 mon fr\u00e8re de partager avec moi notre h\u00e9ritage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.14","name":"Luc 12:14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.12","name":"Luc 12:12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.14","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:14","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>J\u00e9sus lui r\u00e9pondit: <span class=\"wj\">O homme, qui m\u2019a \u00e9tabli pour \u00eatre votre juge, ou pour faire vos partages?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.15","name":"Luc 12:15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.13","name":"Luc 12:13","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.15","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:15","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Puis il leur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Gardez-vous avec soin<\/span><span class=\"wj\">de toute avarice; car la vie d\u2019un homme ne d\u00e9pend pas de ses biens, f\u00fbt-il dans l\u2019abondance.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.16","name":"Luc 12:16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.14","name":"Luc 12:14","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.16","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:16","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Et il leur dit cette parabole: <span class=\"wj\">Les terres d\u2019un homme riche avaient beaucoup rapport\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.17","name":"Luc 12:17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.15","name":"Luc 12:15","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.17","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:17","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et il raisonnait en lui-m\u00eame, disant: Que ferai-je? Car je n\u2019ai pas de place pour serrer ma r\u00e9colte.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.18","name":"Luc 12:18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.16","name":"Luc 12:16","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.18","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:18","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Voici, dit-il, ce que je ferai: j\u2019abattrai mes greniers, j\u2019en b\u00e2tirai de plus grands, j\u2019y amasserai toute ma r\u00e9colte et tous mes biens;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.19","name":"Luc 12:19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.17","name":"Luc 12:17","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.19","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:19","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">et je dirai \u00e0 mon \u00e2me:<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Mon \u00e2me, tu as beaucoup de biens en r\u00e9serve pour plusieurs ann\u00e9es; repose-toi, mange, bois, et r\u00e9jouis-toi.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.20","name":"Luc 12:20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.18","name":"Luc 12:18","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.20","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:20","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais Dieu lui dit:<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Insens\u00e9! Cette nuit m\u00eame ton \u00e2me te sera redemand\u00e9e; et ce que tu as pr\u00e9par\u00e9,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">pour qui cela sera-t-il?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.21","name":"Luc 12:21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.19","name":"Luc 12:19","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.21","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:21","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il en est ainsi de celui qui amasse des tr\u00e9sors pour lui-m\u00eame, et qui n\u2019est pas riche pour Dieu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.22","name":"Luc 12:22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.20","name":"Luc 12:20","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.22","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:22","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.023,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 22-34: cf. Mt 6:19-34. (1 Ti 6:6-8. H\u00e9 13:5.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>J\u00e9sus dit ensuite \u00e0 ses disciples: <span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est pourquoi je vous dis: Ne vous inqui\u00e9tez pas pour votre vie de ce que vous mangerez, ni pour votre corps de quoi vous serez v\u00eatus.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.23","name":"Luc 12:23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.21","name":"Luc 12:21","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.23","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:23","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">La vie est plus que la nourriture, et le corps plus que le v\u00eatement.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.24","name":"Luc 12:24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.22","name":"Luc 12:22","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.24","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:24","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Consid\u00e9rez les corbeaux: ils ne s\u00e8ment ni ne moissonnent, ils n\u2019ont ni cellier ni grenier; et Dieu les nourrit. Combien ne valez-vous pas plus que les oiseaux!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.25","name":"Luc 12:25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.23","name":"Luc 12:23","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.25","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:25","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Qui de vous, par ses inqui\u00e9tudes, peut ajouter une coud\u00e9e \u00e0 la dur\u00e9e de sa vie?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.26","name":"Luc 12:26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.24","name":"Luc 12:24","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.26","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:26","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Si donc vous ne pouvez pas m\u00eame la moindre chose, pourquoi vous inqui\u00e9tez-vous du reste?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.27","name":"Luc 12:27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.25","name":"Luc 12:25","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.27","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:27","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Consid\u00e9rez comment croissent les lis: ils ne travaillent ni ne filent; cependant je vous dis que Salomon m\u00eame, dans toute sa gloire, n\u2019a pas \u00e9t\u00e9 v\u00eatu comme l\u2019un d\u2019eux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.28","name":"Luc 12:28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.26","name":"Luc 12:26","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.28","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:28","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Si Dieu rev\u00eat ainsi l\u2019herbe qui est aujourd\u2019hui dans les champs et qui demain sera jet\u00e9e au four, \u00e0 combien plus forte raison ne vous v\u00eatira-t-il pas, gens de peu de foi?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.29","name":"Luc 12:29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.27","name":"Luc 12:27","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.29","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:29","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et vous, ne cherchez pas ce que vous mangerez et ce que vous boirez, et ne soyez pas inquiets.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.30","name":"Luc 12:30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.28","name":"Luc 12:28","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.30","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:30","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car toutes ces choses, ce sont les pa\u00efens du monde qui les recherchent. Votre P\u00e8re sait que vous en avez besoin.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.31","name":"Luc 12:31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.29","name":"Luc 12:29","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.31","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:31","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Cherchez plut\u00f4t le royaume de Dieu; et toutes ces choses vous seront donn\u00e9es par-dessus.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.32","name":"Luc 12:32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.30","name":"Luc 12:30","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.32","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:32","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ne crains point, petit troupeau; car votre P\u00e8re a trouv\u00e9 bon de vous donner le royaume.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.33","name":"Luc 12:33","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.31","name":"Luc 12:31","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.33","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:33","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Vendez ce que vous poss\u00e9dez, et donnez-le en aum\u00f4nes.<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Faites-vous des bourses qui ne s\u2019usent point, un tr\u00e9sor in\u00e9puisable dans les cieux, o\u00f9 le voleur n\u2019approche point, et o\u00f9 la teigne ne d\u00e9truit point.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.34","name":"Luc 12:34","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.32","name":"Luc 12:32","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.34","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:34","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car l\u00e0 o\u00f9 est votre tr\u00e9sor, l\u00e0 aussi sera votre c\u0153ur.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.35","name":"Luc 12:35","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.33","name":"Luc 12:33","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.35","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:35","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.036,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 35-40: cf. Mc 13:33-37. Mt 24:42-44; 25:1-13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Que vos reins soient ceints, et vos lampes allum\u00e9es.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.36","name":"Luc 12:36","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.34","name":"Luc 12:34","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.36","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:36","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et vous, soyez semblables \u00e0 des hommes qui attendent que leur ma\u00eetre revienne des noces, afin de lui ouvrir d\u00e8s qu\u2019il arrivera et frappera.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.37","name":"Luc 12:37","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.35","name":"Luc 12:35","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.37","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:37","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Heureux ces serviteurs que le ma\u00eetre, \u00e0 son arriv\u00e9e, trouvera veillant! Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, il se ceindra, les fera mettre \u00e0 table, et s\u2019approchera pour les servir.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.38","name":"Luc 12:38","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.36","name":"Luc 12:36","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.38","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:38","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Qu\u2019il arrive \u00e0 la deuxi\u00e8me ou \u00e0 la troisi\u00e8me veille, heureux ces serviteurs, s\u2019il les trouve veillant!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.39","name":"Luc 12:39","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.37","name":"Luc 12:37","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.39","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:39","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Sachez-le bien, si le ma\u00eetre de la maison savait \u00e0 quelle heure le voleur doit venir, il veillerait et ne laisserait pas percer sa maison.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.40","name":"Luc 12:40","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.38","name":"Luc 12:38","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.40","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:40","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Vous aussi, tenez-vous pr\u00eats, car le Fils de l\u2019homme viendra \u00e0 l\u2019heure o\u00f9 vous n\u2019y penserez pas.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.41","name":"Luc 12:41","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.39","name":"Luc 12:39","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.41","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:41","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.042,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 41-48: cf. Mt 24:45-51; 25:14-30.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>Pierre lui dit: Seigneur, est-ce \u00e0 nous, ou \u00e0 tous, que tu adresses cette parabole?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.42","name":"Luc 12:42","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.40","name":"Luc 12:40","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.42","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:42","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>Et le Seigneur dit: <span class=\"wj\">Quel est donc l\u2019\u00e9conome fid\u00e8le et prudent que le ma\u00eetre \u00e9tablira sur ses gens, pour leur donner la nourriture au temps convenable?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.43","name":"Luc 12:43","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.41","name":"Luc 12:41","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.43","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:43","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Heureux ce serviteur, que son ma\u00eetre, \u00e0 son arriv\u00e9e, trouvera faisant ainsi!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.44","name":"Luc 12:44","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.42","name":"Luc 12:42","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.44","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:44","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.045,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, il l\u2019\u00e9tablira sur tous ses biens.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.45","name":"Luc 12:45","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.45"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.43","name":"Luc 12:43","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"45","lastverse":"45","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.45","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.45","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:45","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.044,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.046,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.45\" class=\"v\">45<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais, si ce serviteur dit en lui-m\u00eame: Mon ma\u00eetre tarde \u00e0 venir; s\u2019il se met \u00e0 battre les serviteurs et les servantes, \u00e0 manger, \u00e0 boire et \u00e0 s\u2019enivrer,<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.46","name":"Luc 12:46","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.46"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.44","name":"Luc 12:44","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.44"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"46","lastverse":"46","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.46","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.46","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:46","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.045,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.047,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.46\" class=\"v\">46<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">le ma\u00eetre de ce serviteur viendra le jour o\u00f9 il ne s\u2019y attend pas et \u00e0 l\u2019heure qu\u2019il ne conna\u00eet pas, il le mettra en pi\u00e8ces, et lui donnera sa part avec les infid\u00e8les.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.47","name":"Luc 12:47","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.47"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.45","name":"Luc 12:45","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.45"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"47","lastverse":"47","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.47","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.47","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:47","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.046,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.048,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.47\" class=\"v\">47<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Le serviteur qui, ayant connu la volont\u00e9 de son ma\u00eetre, n\u2019a rien pr\u00e9par\u00e9 et n\u2019a pas agi selon sa volont\u00e9, sera battu d\u2019un grand nombre de coups.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.48","name":"Luc 12:48","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.48"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.46","name":"Luc 12:46","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.46"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"48","lastverse":"48","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.48","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.48","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:48","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.047,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.049,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.48\" class=\"v\">48<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais celui qui, ne l\u2019ayant pas connue, a fait des choses dignes de ch\u00e2timent, sera battu de peu de coups. On demandera beaucoup \u00e0 qui l\u2019on a beaucoup donn\u00e9, et on exigera davantage de celui \u00e0 qui l\u2019on a beaucoup confi\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.49","name":"Luc 12:49","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.49"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.47","name":"Luc 12:47","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.47"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"49","lastverse":"49","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.49","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.49","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:49","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.048,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.050,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 49-53: cf. Mt 10:34-36.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.49\" class=\"v\">49<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je suis venu jeter un feu sur la terre, et qu\u2019ai-je \u00e0 d\u00e9sirer, s\u2019il est d\u00e9j\u00e0 allum\u00e9?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.50","name":"Luc 12:50","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.50"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.48","name":"Luc 12:48","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.48"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"50","lastverse":"50","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.50","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.50","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:50","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.051,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.50\" class=\"v\">50<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Il est un bapt\u00eame dont je dois \u00eatre baptis\u00e9, et combien il me tarde qu\u2019il soit accompli!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.51","name":"Luc 12:51","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.51"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.49","name":"Luc 12:49","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"51","lastverse":"51","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.51","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.51","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:51","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.050,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.052,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.51\" class=\"v\">51<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Pensez-vous que je sois venu apporter la paix sur la terre? Non, vous dis-je,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">mais la division.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.52","name":"Luc 12:52","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.52"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.50","name":"Luc 12:50","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.50"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"52","lastverse":"52","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.52","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.52","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:52","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.051,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.053,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.52\" class=\"v\">52<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car d\u00e9sormais cinq dans une maison seront divis\u00e9s, trois contre deux, et deux contre trois;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.53","name":"Luc 12:53","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.53"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.51","name":"Luc 12:51","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.51"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"53","lastverse":"53","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.53","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.53","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:53","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.052,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.054,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.53\" class=\"v\">53<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">le p\u00e8re contre le fils et le fils contre le p\u00e8re, la m\u00e8re contre la fille et la fille contre la m\u00e8re, la belle-m\u00e8re contre la belle-fille et la belle-fille contre la belle-m\u00e8re.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.54","name":"Luc 12:54","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.54"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.52","name":"Luc 12:52","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.52"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"54","lastverse":"54","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.54","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.54","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:54","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.053,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.055,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 54-59: cf. (Mt 16:1-3; 5:25, 26.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.54\" class=\"v\">54<\/sup>Il dit encore aux foules: <span class=\"wj\">Quand vous voyez un nuage se lever \u00e0 l\u2019occident, vous dites aussit\u00f4t: La pluie vient. Et il arrive ainsi.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.55","name":"Luc 12:55","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.55"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.53","name":"Luc 12:53","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.53"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"55","lastverse":"55","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.55","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.55","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:55","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.054,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.056,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.55\" class=\"v\">55<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et quand vous voyez souffler le vent du midi, vous dites: Il fera chaud. Et cela arrive.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.56","name":"Luc 12:56","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.56"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.54","name":"Luc 12:54","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.54"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"56","lastverse":"56","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.56","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.56","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:56","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.055,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.057,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.56\" class=\"v\">56<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Hypocrites! Vous savez discerner l\u2019aspect de la terre et du ciel; comment ne discernez-vous pas ce temps-ci?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.57","name":"Luc 12:57","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.57"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.55","name":"Luc 12:55","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.55"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"57","lastverse":"57","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.57","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.57","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:57","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.056,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.058,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.57\" class=\"v\">57<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et pourquoi ne discernez-vous pas de vous-m\u00eames ce qui est juste?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.58","name":"Luc 12:58","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.58"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.56","name":"Luc 12:56","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.56"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"58","lastverse":"58","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.58","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.58","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:58","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.057,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.012.059,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.58\" class=\"v\">58<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Lorsque tu vas avec ton adversaire devant le magistrat, t\u00e2che en chemin de te d\u00e9gager de lui, de peur qu\u2019il ne te tra\u00eene devant le juge, que le juge ne te livre \u00e0 l\u2019officier de justice, et que celui-ci ne te mette en prison.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.59","name":"Luc 12:59","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.59"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.57","name":"Luc 12:57","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.57"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"59","lastverse":"59","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.59","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.59","label":"","reference":"Luc 12:59","prev_osis_id":"Luke.012.058,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Luke.013.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Luke.12.59\" class=\"v\">59<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je te le dis, tu ne sortiras pas de l\u00e0 que tu n\u2019aies pay\u00e9 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la derni\u00e8re pite.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Luke.12","name":"Luc 12","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.13.1","name":"Luc 13:1","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.13.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Luke.12.58","name":"Luc 12:58","id":"fra-LSG:Luke.12.58"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc23648a8.35326317');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\